Subject: Access Information Center - Not Reporting Attribute Changes
Description: I am trying to track attribute changes for a user. I am trying to use Access Information Center. However, AIC is not showing or reporting changes to any AD users. I have specific users where I know changes were made but AIC is blank when I look at the "Attribute Changes" in the Reports section for these users.
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
Customer was not seeing attribute changes in the AIC

[Resolution]
Customer was not running differential scans for Active Directory Inventory so attribute changes were not being collect
